Posts.Content: No, but high PSA's can jump around a bit, but this is extreme. As you suspect getting to an experienced Urologist is a must. I suggest finding the nearest teaching medical center with an Urology dept and tell the appointment maker you have a PSA over 60 and you need to see someone today. That Gout attack was a piece of good luck. At least know that this prostate part of the problem can be fixed. All the best.

Posts.Title: High PSA Level Worries

Posts.Content: There is another form of the PSA also a blood test called a "free" PSA. High scores are good, low scores are not good. It is used to confirm the standard PSA results. That said, your standard PSA about doubled in about 2 years. You have a problem. Similar to the problem I had. DO THE BIOPSY! And yes NOW!
